MAP_Conv

library(readxl)
library(ggplot2)

df<- read_xlsx("DT_conv.xlsx")


library(dplyr)
## 
## Attaching package: 'dplyr'
## The following objects are masked from 'package:stats':
## 
##     filter, lag
## The following objects are masked from 'package:base':
## 
##     intersect, setdiff, setequal, union
con<- df

library(leaflet)
df_map <- data.frame(''=con$'', lat=con$'', lng=con$'') 


icIcon <- makeIcon(iconUrl = ".png",
                   iconWidth = 50,
                   iconHeight = 50)
ic_map <-  leaflet() %>% 
  addTiles() %>% 
  addMarkers(lat = df_map$lat,lng=df_map$lng,
             clusterOptions = markerClusterOptions(),
             popup = df_map$,
             icon = icIcon)

ic_map
